        "explanation": "Coefficients $[1, 2, -1, 5]$ with $k = -2$: bring down $1$ → multiply $-2$ → add to $2$ gives $0$ → multiply $0$ → add to $-1$ gives $-1$ → multiply $2$ → add to $5$ gives $7$. $P(-2) = 7$."
      },
